high_descs: Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Cut the potato that is on the counter into slices.
Put the butter knife down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a left and go to the garbage can.
Put the potato slice in the garbage can.
Turn to the right, go to the round black dining table.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table.
Turn to the right, go across the room to the white table.
Cut the potato that is on the table into slices.
Turn around, go forward, turn around to the table.
Put the butter knife down on the table.
Move forward to the table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go to the garbage can across the room.
Put the potato slice into the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put two slices of potato into the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter between the fridge and the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter that is on the spatula.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter on the spatula.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around, head towards the door and then turn left and head to the green trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the trash can.
Turn to the right and approach the black table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn to the right and head to the white table.
Cut the potato on the white table.
Turn to the right and then back to the left to face the white table again.
Put the knife on the white table to the right of the apple.
Look up at the potato on the back of the table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn around and head to the green trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two slices of potato in the trash can.
